---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { useTranslations } from '../../i18n/ui';

const lang = 'en' as const;
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<BaseLayout lang={lang} title={t('about.title')}>
  <h1>{t('about.title')}</h1>
  <p>
    This site focuses on <strong>HCL Domino</strong> and its broader ecosystem (Notes, Domino REST
    API, Volt MX, Nomad, AppDev Pack, and more) — covering the latest news and technical articles.
  </p>
  <p>
    A daily GitHub Actions cron triggers the publishing flow: an LLM drafts each article, a second
    LLM vendor cross-reviews it for factual accuracy (a critical factual issue blocks publication
    and forces a rewrite), and a human engineer adds hands-on context. Topics are drawn from the
    last 24–72 hours of official HCL announcements, HCL Ambassador blogs, and OpenNTF activity —
    when there's no news on a given day, the post is a deep-dive on an under-covered class or
    feature from the official docs instead. Every source is cited at the end of the post.
  </p>
  <p>
    Traditional Chinese and English versions are published together. Every article goes through the
    cross-LLM review and human-checkpoint flow before going live, avoiding the failure modes typical
    of pure AI content. Source code and the full workflow are open on
    <a href="https://github.com/bryanHsiao/domino-news">GitHub</a>.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>
